(DbType = Boolean), @__ef_filter__p_0='?' (DbType = Boolean)], CommandType='Text', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [t1].[BookId] AS [bookId], [t1].[Isbn], [t1].[Name] AS [name], [t1].[GradeId] AS [gradeId], [t2].[Name] AS [gradeName], [t1].[Name0] AS [publisher], [t1].[IsMandatory] AS [mandatory]
FROM [StudentSelectedBooks] AS [s]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT [a].[Id], [a].[BookId], [a].[GradeId], [t].[IsMandatory], [t].[Isbn], [t].[Name], [t0].[Name] AS [Name0]
    FROM [AcademicGradeBooks] AS [a]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [s0].[Id], [s0].[IsMandatory], [s0].[Isbn], [s0].[Name]
        FROM [StudentBooks] AS [s0]
        WHERE (@__ef_filter__p_2 = CAST(1 AS bit)) OR ([s0].[IsDeleted] <> CAST(1 AS bit))
    ) AS [t] ON [a].[BookId] = [t].[Id]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Name]
        FROM [Publishers] AS [p]
        WHERE (@__ef_filter__p_3 = CAST(1 AS bit)) OR ([p].[IsDeleted] <> CAST(1 AS bit))
    ) AS [t0] ON [a].[PublisherId] = [t0].[Id]
    WHERE ((@__ef_filter__p_1 = CAST(1 AS bit)) OR ([a].[IsDeleted] <> CAST(1 AS bit))) AND (((((@__input_filter_0 LIKE N'') OR (CHARINDEX(@__input_filter_0, [t].[Name]) > 0)) OR ((@__input_filter_0 LIKE N'') OR (CHARINDEX(@__input_filter_0, [t].[Isbn]) > 0))) OR ((@__input_filter_0 LIKE N'') OR (CHARINDEX(@__input_filter_0, [t0].[Name]) > 0))) AND ([a].[GradeId] = @__input_gradId_1))

FROM [StudentBooks] AS [s]
INNER JOIN (

    FROM [AcademicGradeBooks] AS [a]
    WHERE (@__ef_filter__p_1 = CAST(1 AS bit)) OR ([a].[IsDeleted] <> CAST(1 AS bit))
) AS [t] ON [s].[Id] = [t].[BookId]

    SELECT [s].[Id], [s].[CreationTime], [s].[CreatorUserId], [s].[DeleterUserId], [s].[DeletionTime], [s].[FamilyName], [s].[FamilyNameAr], [s].[IsDeleted], [s].[LastModificationTime], [s].[LastModifierUserId], [s].[Name], [s].[NameAr], [s].[StudentCode], [s].[UserId]
    FROM [Students] AS [s]
    WHERE (@__ef_filter__p_1 = CAST(1 AS bit)) OR ([s].[IsDeleted] <> CAST(1 AS bit))
) AS [t] ON [a].[StudentId] = [t].[Id]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT [a0].[Id], [a0].[AcademicYearId], [a0].[ClassId], [a0].[CreationTime], [a0].[CreatorUserId], [a0].[DeleterUserId], [a0].[DeletionTime], [a0].[GradeId], [a0].[IsDeleted], [a0].[LastModificationTime], [a0].[LastModifierUserId]
    FROM [AcademicGradeClasses] AS [a0]
    WHERE (@__ef_filter__p_2 = CAST(1 AS bit)) OR ([a0].[IsDeleted] <> CAST(1 AS bit))
) AS [t0] ON [a].[AcademicGradeClassId] = [t0].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [g].[Id], [g].[CreationTime], [g].[CreatorUserId], [g].[DeleterUserId], [g].[DeletionTime], [g].[IsDeleted], [g].[LastModificationTime], [g].[LastModifierUserId], [g].[Name], [g].[NameAr], [g].[StudyOrder]
    FROM [Grades] AS [g]
    WHERE (@__ef_filter__p_3 = CAST(1 AS bit)) OR ([g].[IsDeleted] <> CAST(1 AS bit))
) AS [t1] ON [t0].[GradeId] = [t1].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[Id], [c].[CreationTime], [c].[CreatorUserId], [c].[DeleterUserId], [c].[DeletionTime], [c].[GradeId], [c].[IsDeleted], [c].[LastModificationTime], [c].[LastModifierUserId], [c].[Name], [c].[NameAr]
    FROM [Classes] AS [c]
    WHERE (@__ef_filter__p_4 = CAST(1 AS bit)) OR ([c].[IsDeleted] <> CAST(1 AS bit))
) AS [t2] ON [t0].[ClassId] = [t2].[Id]
WHERE (@__ef_filter__p_0 = CAST(1 AS bit)) OR ([a].[IsDeleted] <> CAST(1 AS bit))

    SELECT [a].[Id], [a].[BookId], [a].[GradeId], [a].[PublisherId]
    FROM [AcademicGradeBooks] AS [a]
    WHERE (@__ef_filter__p_1 = CAST(1 AS bit)) OR ([a].[IsDeleted] <> CAST(1 AS bit))
) AS [t] ON [s].[AcademicGradeBookId] = [t].[Id]

    WHERE (@__ef_filter__p_2 = CAST(1 AS bit)) OR ([s0].[IsDeleted] <> CAST(1 AS bit))
) AS [t0] ON [t].[BookId] = [t0].[Id]

    SELECT [a].[BookId], [a].[GradeId], [a].[PublisherId]
    FROM [AcademicGradeBooks] AS [a]
    WHERE (@__ef_filter__p_1 = CAST(1 AS bit)) OR ([a].[IsDeleted] <> CAST(1 AS bit))
) AS [t] ON [s].[Id] = [t].[BookId]

    SELECT [g].[Id], [g].[Name]
    FROM [Grades] AS [g]
    WHERE (@__ef_filter__p_2 = CAST(1 AS bit)) OR ([g].[IsDeleted] <> CAST(1 AS bit))
) AS [t0] ON [t].[GradeId] = [t0].[Id]

    FROM [Publishers] AS [p]
    WHERE (@__ef_filter__p_3 = CAST(1 AS bit)) OR ([p].[IsDeleted] <> CAST(1 AS bit))
) AS [t1] ON [t].[PublisherId] = [t1].[Id]

    SELECT [g].[Id], [g].[CreationTime], [g].[CreatorUserId], [g].[DeleterUserId], [g].[DeletionTime], [g].[IsDeleted], [g].[LastModificationTime], [g].[LastModifierUserId], [g].[Name], [g].[NameAr], [g].[StudyOrder]
    FROM [Grades] AS [g]
    WHERE (@__ef_filter__p_3 = CAST(1 AS bit)) OR ([g].[IsDeleted] <> CAST(1 AS bit))
) AS [t1] ON [t0].[GradeId] = [t1].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[Id], [c].[CreationTime], [c].[CreatorUserId], [c].[DeleterUserId], [c].[DeletionTime], [c].[GradeId], [c].[IsDeleted], [c].[LastModificationTime], [c].[LastModifierUserId], [c].[Name], [c].[NameAr]
    FROM [Classes] AS [c]
    WHERE (@__ef_filter__p_4 = CAST(1 AS bit)) OR ([c].[IsDeleted] <> CAST(1 AS bit))
) AS [t2] ON [t0].[ClassId] = [t2].[Id]
WHERE (@__ef_filter__p_0 = CAST(1 AS bit)) OR ([a].[IsDeleted] <> CAST(1 AS bit))

SELECT [a].[Id], [a].[AcademicGradeClassId], [a].[CreationTime], [a].[CreatorUserId], [a].[DeleterUserId], [a].[DeletionTime], [a].[IsDeleted], [a].[LastModificationTime], [a].[LastModifierUserId], [a].[StudentId], [t].[Id], [t].[CreationTime], [t].[CreatorUserId], [t].[DeleterUserId], [t].[DeletionTime], [t].[FamilyName], [t].[FamilyNameAr], [t].[IsDeleted], [t].[LastModificationTime], [t].[LastModifierUserId], [t].[Name], [t].[NameAr], [t].[StudentCode], [t].[UserId], [t0].[Id], [t0].[AcademicYearId], [t0].[ClassId], [t0].[CreationTime], [t0].[CreatorUserId], [t0].[DeleterUserId], [t0].[DeletionTime], [t0].[GradeId], [t0].[IsDeleted], [t0].[LastModificationTime], [t0].[LastModifierUserId], [t1].[Id], [t1].[CreationTime], [t1].[CreatorUserId], [t1].[DeleterUserId], [t1].[DeletionTime], [t1].[IsDeleted], [t1].[LastModificationTime], [t1].[LastModifierUserId], [t1].[Name], [t1].[NameAr], [t1].[StudyOrder], [t2].[Id], [t2].[CreationTime], [t2].[CreatorUserId], [t2].[DeleterUserId], [t2].[DeletionTime], [t2].[GradeId], [t2].[IsDeleted], [t2].[LastModificationTime], [t2].[LastModifierUserId], [t2].[Name], [t2].[NameAr]
FROM [AcademicStudents] AS [a]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT [s].[Id], [s].[CreationTime], [s].[CreatorUserId], [s].[DeleterUserId], [s].[DeletionTime], [s].[FamilyName], [s].[FamilyNameAr], [s].[IsDeleted], [s].[LastModificationTime], [s].[LastModifierUserId], [s].[Name], [s].[NameAr], [s].[StudentCode], [s].[UserId]
    FROM [Students] AS [s]
    WHERE (@__ef_filter__p_1 = CAST(1 AS bit)) OR ([s].[IsDeleted] <> CAST(1 AS bit))
) AS [t] ON [a].[StudentId] = [t].[Id]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT [a0].[Id], [a0].[AcademicYearId], [a0].[ClassId], [a0].[CreationTime], [a0].[CreatorUserId], [a0].[DeleterUserId], [a0].[DeletionTime], [a0].[GradeId], [a0].[IsDeleted], [a0].[LastModificationTime], [a0].[LastModifierUserId]
    FROM [AcademicGradeClasses] AS [a0]
    WHERE (@__ef_filter__p_2 = CAST(1 AS bit)) OR ([a0].[IsDeleted] <> CAST(1 AS bit))
) AS [t0] ON [a].[AcademicGradeClassId] = [t0].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [g].[Id], [g].[CreationTime], [g].[CreatorUserId], [g].[DeleterUserId], [g].[DeletionTime], [g].[IsDeleted], [g].[LastModificationTime], [g].[LastModifierUserId], [g].[Name], [g].[NameAr], [g].[StudyOrder]
    FROM [Grades] AS [g]
    WHERE (@__ef_filter__p_3 = CAST(1 AS bit)) OR ([g].[IsDeleted] <> CAST(1 AS bit))
) AS [t1] ON [t0].[GradeId] = [t1].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[Id], [c].[CreationTime], [c].[CreatorUserId], [c].[DeleterUserId], [c].[DeletionTime], [c].[GradeId], [c].[IsDeleted], [c].[LastModificationTime], [c].[LastModifierUserId], [c].[Name], [c].[NameAr]
    FROM [Classes] AS [c]
    WHERE (@__ef_filter__p_4 = CAST(1 AS bit)) OR ([c].[IsDeleted] <> CAST(1 AS bit))
) AS [t2] ON [t0].[ClassId] = [t2].[Id]
WHERE (@__ef_filter__p_0 = CAST(1 AS bit)) OR ([a].[IsDeleted] <> CAST(1 AS bit))
